snippet.title: Reverse Collapse: Code Name Bakery World Premiere Trailer
snippet.description:
The new Tactical RPG game ---- Reverse Collapse: Code Name Bakery from Sunborn Network is coming to Steam, Nintendo Switch and mobile. Re-collapse is a completely rebuilt and improved version of the original “Code Name: Bakery Girl”, which share the same universe as Girls’ Frontline. 

Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1127700/Reverse_Collapse_Code_Name_Bakery/
